data.description: Welcome home to this spacious 5 bedroom/3 bath home in a quiet culdesac! The open concept living and dining room provides an inviting space for gatherings and entertaining. Enjoy family time in the kitchen which adjoins the cozy family room with fireplace! Spacious master suite with separate his and hers closets! Take in the beauty of the outdoors from your enclosed patio or open deck with plenty of room in the large fenced backyard perfect for family activities or pets. Oversized garage with workshop/office perfect for all of those home projects! All of this in a great location with easy access to downtown Raleigh, White Oak shopping centers, and major thoroughfares. Schedule a showing today!
